---
// src/components/FitCriteria.astro
---

<section class="criteria-section">
  <div class="criteria-container">
    <div class="criteria-intro">
      <h2 class="criteria-heading">Engagement Framework: Screening for Fit</h2>
      <p class="criteria-lead">
        We do not accept every engagement. AI integration within enterprise
        customer experience is fundamentally an operational risk, not a software
        purchase. We screen potential partners against strict operational
        baselines to guarantee measurable execution.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="criteria-split">
      <!-- Who We Partner With -->
      <div class="criteria-block alignment-positive">
        <h3>Minimum Requirements for Engagement</h3>
        <ul class="criteria-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Complex Legacy Infrastructures:</strong> Organizations managing
            multi-layered stakeholder environments where customer-facing friction
            directly impacts retention.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Data Maturity Baseline:</strong> Businesses with established Salesforce
            or enterprise CRM data structures ready to be translated into automated
            workflows.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Executive Mandate:</strong> Leadership teams who recognize that
            AI success is an adoption and trust problem, requiring cross-functional
            authority to execute.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Who We Do Not Serve -->
      <div class="criteria-block alignment-negative">
        <h3>Out of Scope Environments</h3>
        <ul class="criteria-list">
          <li>
            <strong>"Plug-and-Play" Expectations:</strong> We do not serve organizations
            looking for surface-level API wrappers or immediate, un-measured automation
            patches.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Siloed Technical Projects:</strong> Engagements treated strictly
            as isolated IT tasks without active frontline workflow adoption strategy
            are rejected.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Commodity Procurement:</strong> Our pricing reflects systemic
            operational outcomes, not line-item development hours.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* --- DESIGN TOKENS (Spectrum 2 Elegant & Minimalist Scale) --- */
  .criteria-section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background-color: var(--spectrum-background-layer-2, #f5f5f5);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 10%);
  }

  .criteria-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 56px;
  }

  .criteria-intro {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .criteria-heading {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .criteria-lead {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #4b4b4b);
  }

  /* --- SPLIT LAYOUT --- */
  .criteria-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .criteria-block {
    background-color: var(--spectrum-background-layer-1, #ffffff);
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 10%);
  }

  .criteria-block h3 {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .alignment-positive h3 {
    color: var(--spectrum-global-color-accent, #0265dc);
  }

  .alignment-negative h3 {
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
  }

  .criteria-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .criteria-list li {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #4b4b4b);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  /* Custom minimal list indicators mapping to Spectrum aesthetics */
  .criteria-list li::before {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 50%);
  }

  .alignment-positive .criteria-list li::before {
    color: var(--spectrum-global-color-accent, #0265dc);
  }

  /* --- 📱 RESPONSIVE MEDIA QUERIES --- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .criteria-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .criteria-section {
      padding: 64px 16px;
    }

    .criteria-heading {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .criteria-block {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
